1. Connect to database: D:/src/MongoDB/mongodb/bin/mongod.exe --dbpath=D:/src/MongoDB/mongodatabases

2. Run Nodemon from dev: npm run dev


3. For Ngrok connection via cmd: ngrok http --domain=conversely-inviting-gelding.ngrok-free.app 3000


for memory issues (audio upload) => $ export NODE_OPTIONS=--max_old_space_size=4096
                                    $ npm run build:static